{"tid":1760361,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［蘋果快啲俾返錢啦］今日又無俾錢就用左人地張相做封面","createTime":"2019-11-28T07:06:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T08:20:54.000Z","uid":22556,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7ca9bac3e9e9ee99c42dff32b2bdb69e90d23601","tid":1760361,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T07:06:36.000Z","msg":"［蘋果日報未比錢就用咗我張相］<br />\n<br />\n呢件事情得到關注，仲上埋頭條，係好事嚟，但係呢蘋果日報未比錢用咗張相，姐係蘋果日報係收緊幾百蚊月費，係商業機構，而我做記者唔係正職咁pay，因為有另外幾間都同我deal緊買相事宜，宜家姐係唔洗傾，全部deal都會call off 咗，一蚊都冇。你就咁係網上拎咗low res相去印頭版（好唔靚囉），好唔專重freelancer 記者。<br />\n<br />\n之前都有蘋果記者問拎相做網上版，開咗價錢，但係最後已讀不回，最後網上版cap咗圖就當買咗相，最後拎埋去印頭版相，大佬啊，你哋收咁多月費，就咁搶咗freelance記者啲相。<br />\n<br />\n有人就用手機影咗一張中聯辦相就收人二百萬，真係發掘真相，就被人偷咗成果，唉。<br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n近日前線衝突愈發激烈，警察針對記者施暴，我們有攝影師累累受傷，也有攝影器材損壞，決定發起一次小眾籌。你們的小小支持，都是我們走上前線紀實的原動力。 Paypal: <a href=\"http://paypal.me/KSSolutionHK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpaypal.me%2FKSSolutionHK&d=gSA20A4kU26EBUHkB65AtPSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=fceb403d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://paypal.me/KSSolutionHK</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/258321577624896/posts/1357475134376196?d=n&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F258321577624896%2Fposts%2F1357475134376196%3Fd%3Dn%26sfns%3Dmo&d=gSA20A4kU26EBUHkB65AtPSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=f207dfec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/258321577624896/posts/1357475134376196?d=n&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"6a1b0fbc94acad56fc275fef455b73c9f37f2cc2","tid":1760361,"uid":38383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T07:08:52.000Z","msg":"不完美 要改善"},{"pid":"f50ec7f93f3353d2b6a31dda67d86464fcfa9189","tid":1760361,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T07:13:41.000Z","msg":"收月費就尊重下版權&copy;️<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35d7c149a77813e2d47e17ee3fc38c2c6153d